data.description: Welcome Lehigh Acres! This single family home is the Jasper Builders Model by Avantgarde: The Building Group!  This home features three bedrooms plus a den that can easily be converted into a 4th bedroom if desired. Upgrades include plank tile throughout, upgraded granite in kitchen and baths, upgraded glass tile backsplash, upgraded lighting and fan package, upgraded window blinds, upgraded stainless steel appliances to complete the beautiful kitchen. Garage has upgraded epoxy flooring and this property even comes with large screened in back lanai!
